<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>الثّاء والميم<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">مث:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">المَثُّ:</span> مَسْحُكَ أصَابِعَكَ بمِنْدِيْلٍ ونَحْوِه من دَسَمٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">ويُقال للرَّجُلِ الأكُوْلِ:</span> إنَّه لَيَمُثُّ كأنَّه زِقٌّ من سِمَنِه.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وهُوَ مَثٌّ من الرِّجَالِ:</span> أي لَيِّنٌ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">والمِثَاثُ:</span> الدُّهْنُ الذي يُدْهَنُ به الجُرْحُ.<span class="c5"> والمِمَثَّةُ:</span> تِلْكَ الصُّوْفَةُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">ومَثَثْتُ الدَّمْعَ:</span> مَسَحْته.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">والمَثْمَثَةُ:</span> الرَّشْحُ من زِقٍّ أو نَحْيٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">ومَثْمَثْتُه في الماءِ:</span> غَطَطْتُه.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">والمَثْمَثَةُ:</span> التَّخْلِيْطُ. وأنْ لا يُجَادَ العَمَلُ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">وتَمَثْمَثَ عَنّي:</span> أبْطَأَ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">والمَثْمَثَةُ:</span> المَقَامُ والتَّلَبُّثُ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">ثم:</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">ثَمَّ:</span> مَعْنَاه هُنَاكَ؛ للتَّبْعِيْدِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c5">وثُمَّ:</span> حَرْفُ عَطْفٍ؛ وهو للتَّرَاخي،<span class="c5"> ويُقالُ:</span> ثُمَّتَ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c5">والثُّمَّةُ:</span> قَبْضَةٌ من حَشِيْشٍ. وأطْرَافُ الشَّجَرِ بِوَرَقِه يُغْسَلُ به.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c5">وثُمَّ الشَّيْءُ:</span> حُشِيَ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c5">وثَمَّمْتُ الوَطْبَ تَثْمِيْماً:</span> إذا جَعَلْتَ تَحْتَه ثُمَّةً.<span class="c5"> والثُّمَّةُ:</span> الوَضَمُ.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>